{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_main_08-15_beg","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":28,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_main_08-14_end","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"JT8-1","storyName":"恨火，流向原野","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"残忍与歹毒成为一种常态，人们不会恐惧以道德为名的审判，是非不分，善恶不再。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_08-15_beg","avgTag":"行动前","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_08-15","minState":"PLAYED","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":26,"next":28,"characters":["感染者战士","塔露拉","？？？","乌萨斯农民"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":2},{"type":"Dialog","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_iceforest_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":5},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$drift_intro","key":"$drift_loop","volume":"0.4","id":8,"musicid":0},{"type":"Dialog","id":9},{"type":"Character","id":10},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":11},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":12},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"这里就是了。","id":13,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"......塔露拉......你可以不管这事儿的，这台感染者牵引车失踪已经几个月了，可能就是被纠察队截住了而已，我们没什么可做的。","id":14,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"即使是找到遗体，也是给其他人的交代。","id":16,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"要是侦察员没弄错的话，他们失踪的地方，大概就是在这附近。","id":18,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"......","id":19,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"塔露拉！别想了。别想那些胡说八道了。","id":20,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我没有。","id":22,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":23},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"这些没心没肺的家伙......别管他们！","id":24,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"他们根本就没有走下去、走出雪原的决心！和你一起打过仗，怎么会不知道你才是最不怕死的那个？！","id":25,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"塔露拉，相信我，我们都是愿意追随你的！","id":26,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"博卓卡斯替大尉不也是乌萨斯帝国的军人吗？但大家都知道他才是我们最坚定的战士！所有人都信他！","id":27,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":28},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"可不一定。只是因为他太强，太坚固了，那些不相信的人还不敢这么说。","id":29,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"信任的崩塌只是一瞬间的事情。如果有一天，相信爱国者的人都死了，那么后来人还会不会像他原来的追随者那样坚定？","id":30,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"流言会摧毁他人。在没有流言蜚语之前，清白的人是清白的，将信将疑的人也是清白的。","id":31,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"流言出现以后，就没有人是清白的了。","id":32,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"可是，可是你出身怎么样又有什么关系？！你为他们流了多少血？！","id":34,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"没事的。别着急。","id":36,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"而且我还没来及为他们流多少血。","id":37,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":38},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"哎......不要这么说。","id":39,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"你确定要一个人去？浮士德最近已经跟在一些用弓弩的人身边了，他成长得很快，游击队不在，你也可以和他们一起去......","id":40,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"2","id":41},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"保护其他同行的感染者才是最重要的。我们不是为了打仗而去打仗，我们到头来就是想让其他同胞能够活下去。不能本末倒置。","id":42,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"他们的命才是最重要的。","id":43,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"一定要把这个想法一直传递下去。","id":44,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_080","name2":"avg_npc_078","focus":"1","id":45},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"感染者战士","text":"那你......保重。","id":46,"figure":"avg_npc_080"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"放心吧。只是要和当地人交涉而已，不会有什么问题的。","id":48,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialog","id":49},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":50},{"type":"Background","image":"bg_snowconutry_1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":51},{"type":"Character","id":52},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":53},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":54},{"type":"Text","text":"附近的小村落","id":55},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":56},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":58,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"要是以前的我，一定就径直走进去问了。","id":59,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"从什么时候开始变成现在这样子？","id":60,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"东躲西藏，偷偷摸摸......不信任和提防已经逐渐演化成敌意。","id":61,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我是在害怕意外发生，还是在害怕悲剧重演......？","id":62,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"贫瘠的村子。似乎今年的收成也不好。人人脸上都挂着疲倦的神情。","id":63,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialog","id":64},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":65},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":66},{"type":"Character","id":67},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":68},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078","id":69},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"奇怪，这村子应该很久没有迁移了，村口却能看到多处牵引车刮擦的痕迹。","id":70,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"装配处的废材料......应该不是村子废弃的旧牵引车。验证盒不见了。如果是村子自己的车，没必要拿走验证盒......","id":71,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"快入夜了。去垃圾场看看会好一些。","id":72,"figure":"avg_npc_078"},{"type":"Dialog","id":73},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":74},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_walk_n","id":75},{"type":"Character","id":76},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":77},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":78},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":79},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不对劲。除了日常垃圾以外，没再看到任何垃圾残余了。","id":80,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"处理耗尽源石的仪器一台也没见到。不放在垃圾场，会放到哪里去了？","id":81,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"本来在入冬后随处可见的麦秆残渣和暖草草壳也没了。粮食出了问题吗？","id":82,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......不对......不对。是一起烧掉了。有必要去粮仓看看。","id":83,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":84},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":85},{"type":"Character","id":86},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_35","x":"0","y":"20","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","id":87},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":88},{"type":"Character","id":89},{"type":"ImageTween","yFrom":"20","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"40","block":"false","id":90},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"$nervous_loop","volume":"0.4","id":91,"musicid":1},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"怎么回事？怎么......怎么回事？","id":92},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"沉积的源石碎屑......刨得坑坑洼洼的地面。","id":93},{"type":"Dialog","id":94},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":95},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_36","x":"0","y":"20","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","id":96},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":97},{"type":"Character","id":98},{"type":"ImageTween","yFrom":"20","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"40","block":"false","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"啊，抓痕，粮仓门上的抓痕——","id":100},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"啊——！","id":101},{"type":"Dialog","id":102},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":103},{"type":"Image","fadetime":"0","id":104},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":105},{"type":"Dialog","id":106},{"type":"Character","id":107},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"？？？","text":"干什么的？！","id":108},{"type":"Dialog","id":109},{"type":"Character","id":110},{"type":"Text","text":"塔露拉回过身。","id":111},{"type":"Dialog","id":112},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":113},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":114},{"type":"Text","text":"看见塔露拉的穿着，乌萨斯农民放下了手中的铁铲。","id":115},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":116},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"老爷......您这是怎么了？怎么进村子都不说一声？","id":117,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":118},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":119,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":120},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"老爷来这是做什么的？以前从没见过您......是宪兵吗？","id":121,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"还是说，您是来收租的？我们的源石税和粮食，全给征税官啦！拿不出什么东西了。","id":122,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我是来调查一些感染者的。","id":124,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":125},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"啊。感染者？我们村子里是没有感染者的。","id":126,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":127},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那有感染者路过这里吗？","id":128,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":129},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"没有。","id":130,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":131},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我们接到过讯息。的确有感染者从这里路过。识相点。","id":132,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":133},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"啊，老爷，瞒不住您！","id":134,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"这些混账东西，明明说过没任何人知道他们从这走的。","id":135,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":136},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":137,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"所以说的确有。","id":138,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":139},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"是的，他们各个都拿着可怕的武器，可吓人了！","id":140,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"我们不敢反抗他们，也没敢拦他们。","id":141,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"之后他们还抢了我们的粮食。可恶啊，太可恨了，老爷，你一定得抓到这些为非作歹的感染者啊......","id":142,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"stopmusic","fadetime":"3","id":143},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#8","id":144},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不对。","id":145,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不对......","id":146,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#5","id":147},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"不！","id":148,"figure":"avg_npc_078#5"},{"type":"playMusic","intro":"$plot_intro","key":"$plot_loop","volume":"0.4","id":149,"musicid":2},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们怎么敢这么说？","id":150,"figure":"avg_npc_078#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#8","id":151},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们怎么敢这么说......","id":152,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#9","id":153},{"type":"ImageTween","yFrom":"20","yTo":"0","xScaleFrom":"1","yScaleFrom":"1","xScaleTo":"1.1","yScaleTo":"1.1","duration":"40","block":"false","id":154},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们怎么敢这么说！","id":155,"figure":"avg_npc_078#9"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":156},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"啊？","id":157,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"老爷......？您怎么了？","id":158,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#5","id":159},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你听见他们哭喊了！","id":160,"figure":"avg_npc_078#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你听见他们喊救命......","id":161,"figure":"avg_npc_078#5"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你听得见他们手指刮刨仓库大门的声音！","id":162,"figure":"avg_npc_078#5"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":163},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"怎，怎么......老爷......","id":164,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"你没中邪吧？","id":165,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"喂，你们快过来！","id":166,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"你们见过她吗？她是哪里的人？","id":167,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"对，我没听过她的口音！","id":168,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"......是啊！她没带防护面具......调查感染者的官员怎么可能不戴护具？","id":169,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"你到底是谁？！","id":170,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":171},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"......","id":172,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":173},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"问你话呢！","id":174,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":175},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"感染者。","id":176,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":177},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"嗯？","id":178,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":179},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我和被你们害死的那些人一样，是感染者。","id":180,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":181},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"......","id":182,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"我们没做错什么。","id":183,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":184},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你把他们关在这里。你让他们困死在这。","id":185,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":186},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"我有什么办法？我们也一点粮食都没有了！","id":187,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":188},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你可以赶走他们。你可以不让他们进村......哪怕你直接攻击他们，杀了他们，我都不会多说一个字。","id":189,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"但你们欺骗他们，让他们待在空无一物的仓库里，锁上大门，活活饿死他们。","id":190,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"他们饿得连法术都用不了......他们乞求般地来到这里。他们不想攻击你们，没有反抗的力气，他们只是些普通人。","id":191,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":192},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"感染者是什么普通人？！","id":193,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"听好了，你这个感染了的死烂样子......你也懂道理！你知道自己是个怎么样的怪胎对吧？","id":194,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":195},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们封闭仓库，直到源石结晶稳定下来，将他们的尸体和各种干涸源石一起处理了......","id":196,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"他们有家人，有亲人，有想去的地方......他们尸骨无存。感染者是经常尸骨无存，可现在，连他们的灰烬飘向何方，我们都没法再知道。","id":197,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":198},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"我们有什么办法？我们也没吃没喝，我们也过得很惨！","id":199,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"1","id":200},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们为什么要骗他们？","id":201,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","name2":"avg_npc_081","focus":"2","id":202},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"......","id":203,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"你在说什么？","id":204,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"谁知道感染者会怎么样？我们又能怎么办？","id":205,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":206},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"借口。你看见他们饿成那样......你看见他们手无寸铁。","id":207,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你这么做仅仅是因为这么做......很方便。","id":208,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们从一开始就......不。哈。","id":209,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"即使来到这里的不是感染者是普通人，你们也会做一样的事。","id":210,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":211},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"......","id":212,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"（得把她处理了。去叫哨兵！）","id":213,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":214},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——","id":215,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":216},{"type":"Character","id":217},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":218},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":219},{"type":"Character","id":220},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你会看到，你投入了一切的这片大地并不想要你。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":221},{"type":"Subtitle","id":222},{"type":"Text","text":"不。不。","id":223},{"type":"Dialog","id":224},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":225},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":226},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"——","id":227,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":228},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"那你想做什么？事情都发生了，对不起，感染者老爷。","id":229,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"不过我们也可以当你没来过，就像当之前那些人没来过一样......你只要走就行了。","id":230,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":231},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们当他们是什么？","id":232,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":233},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"啊？你是什么，他们就是什么。","id":234,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":235},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"你们当他们是弱者，那我就是不知如何反抗的弱者。","id":236,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_081","id":237},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"乌萨斯农民","text":"......呃......感染者老爷！行行好，我们只是不想惹事！","id":238,"figure":"avg_npc_081"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#4","id":239},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"那他们求你的时候，你们是什么反应？","id":240,"figure":"avg_npc_078#4"},{"type":"Dialog","id":241},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":242},{"type":"Character","id":243},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":244},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":245},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":246},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_1","x":"40","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":247},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":248},{"type":"image","id":249},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_thunders_amb","volume":"0.5","id":250},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你会看见你的所想所为化作乌有。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":251},{"type":"Subtitle","id":252},{"type":"Text","text":"不。","id":253},{"type":"Dialog","id":254},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"false","id":255},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#8","id":256},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我憎恨你们这些卑劣的人。","id":257,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"只要你们还活在这片大地上，这片大地就永无宁日。","id":258,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"感染者纠察官已经三年没来过你们的村子。","id":259,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"拥有这几个聚落的贵族早在大叛乱中丧生，局势混乱不堪，你们的村子已经多年无人管理。","id":260,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"就在这样的情况下......你们......自然而然地......害死了和你们毫无利害关系的人。","id":261,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"只要你们心存一点点善意......你们一样可以放走他们。整个村子听着他们的哀嚎无动于衷，直到他们死去。","id":262,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"但凡还有一丁点善意存在，你们就不会如此恶毒。","id":263,"figure":"avg_npc_078#8"},{"type":"Character","name":"avg_npc_078#9","id":264},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"塔露拉","text":"我恨你们。","id":265,"figure":"avg_npc_078#9"},{"type":"Dialog","id":266},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":267},{"type":"Character","id":268},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":269},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_1","x":"40","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":270},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":271},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":272},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_1","x":"40","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":273},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":274},{"type":"image","id":275},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":276},{"type":"Subtitle","text":"你会看见他们唾弃你所尊敬的一切，生命、尊严和理念都毫无意义。","x":"200","y":"360","alignment":"left","size":"24","delay":"0.04","width":"1280","id":277},{"type":"Subtitle","id":278},{"type":"dialog","id":279},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":280},{"type":"Character","id":281},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$d_gen_thunders_amb","volume":"0.5","id":282},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":283},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_8_1","x":"40","y":"0","xScale":"1.1","yScale":"1.1","fadetime":"0","id":284},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.5","block":"true","id":285},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.7","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":286},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.1","block":"true","id":287},{"type":"image","id":288},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0.3","r":"1","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"4","block":"false","id":289},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$firestorm","volume":"1","text":"","id":290},{"type":"PlaySound","key":"$burningloop1","volume":"1","loop":"true","text":"","id":291},{"type":"Text","text":"不！！","id":292},{"type":"delay","time":"2","id":293},{"type":"Dialog","id":294},{"type":"Blocker","id":295},{"type":"Image","id":296}],"characters":["感染者战士","塔露拉","？？？","乌萨斯农民"]}